dct_title_s: North Pacific Ocean, Marianas--Saipan Island, Saipan Harbor
dct_description_sm: From a survey by U.S.S. Bowditch in 1944. topography is mainly from Japanese government charts.
Relief shown by spot heights; depths shown by isolines and soundings.
